    },
    {
        "Robert Bordens": "Robert Borden"
    },
    {
        "proposal for a ": null
    },
    {
        "Union Government": "Union Government"
    },
    {
        " that would include both Conservatives and Liberals, fearing that this would ultimately hurt the Conservative Party; he was proven to be correct in this analysis. While he campaigned for Conservative candidates in the ": null
    },
    {
        "1917 federal election": "1917 Canadian Federal Election"
